EDUCATIONAL USE DISCLAIMER

This repository and all its contents were created strictly for educational 
and research purposes within an isolated, controlled lab environment.

All systems targeted during this assessment were owned and operated solely 
by the author. No unauthorized systems, networks, or data were accessed at 
any point during the creation of this project.

The techniques, tools, and methodologies documented here are intended to 
support learning in the field of cybersecurity, specifically:

  - Security Operations Center (SOC) analysis
  - Penetration testing fundamentals
  - SIEM detection engineering
  - Incident response procedures

Unauthorized use of these techniques against systems you do not own or have 
explicit written permission to test is illegal and unethical. The author 
assumes no responsibility for misuse of any information contained in this 
repository.

Always practice cybersecurity ethically and legally.

